window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A magic user on the run. A sleepy small town filled with shifters, witches and vampires. Will Lucas find refuge, a fated mate, or death?</b><br> <br> Lucas used to be a normal person. Was it really so bad that he had a job he didn't like, and he still lived with his parents? At least he didn't have balls of light shooting out of him. Oh wait. Yes, he does. And he's not sure why it's happening or what to do about it. But it gets worse. Way worse and deadlier than Lucas had ever thought possible.<br> <br> Running for his life, he ends up in a small town named Saint Lakes and right into the arms of a dragon shifter who claims to be his fated mate.<br> <br> Bennett enjoys his life as a boat mechanic in his sleepy hometown. He isn't looking for disruptions. When Lucas comes to town, the last thing he expects is for the sweet, smaller man to be is a witch. He also doesn't expect blood thirsty vampires either. Bennett will risk everything to protect his town, his clan, and his heart.<br> <br> Everyone wants a piece of the witch. It's up to Bennett to keep him safe, but how can he when the enemy keeps getting closer.<br> <br> Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
